WHEREAS, Chef DiGrazia has further distinguished herself through her service as
a culinary ambassador, having prepared and presented cuisine for members of the Louisiana
Senate and other civic leaders, thereby strengthening connections between culture,
governance, and community pride; and
WHEREAS, her journey to becoming a thriving culinary entrepreneur in Louisiana
stands as a testament to Chef DiGrazia's perseverance, innovation, and the powerful role of
cultural heritage in shaping communities in Louisiana.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend and express deep appreciation for Chef Niematulai DiGrazia's
ongoing work as a culinary ambassador contributing to Louisiana's ongoing legacy as a
culinary destination, as well as her culinary contributions to the state of Louisiana.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Chef
Niematulai DiGrazia.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
